item.title: Australia Entry #16 - February 23rd - March 22nd, 2025
item.description: Seeing Friends in Sydney Near the end of February, a few of my friends from back in the states flew out to Australia and so I made sure that I went out to Sydney to meet them and have a fun few days with my best friends.
